Relevant issue: https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/80735

Not quite sure how to diagnose this more specifically. I know it's a Rust problem, not an emulator problem, because where it fails is consistent, but other than that, I'm really not sure. Appears to call abort (from abort.c).
Looks like crt-static for riscv64 doesn't use crt1.o...?
